@page "/"

<h2>📚 Book Catalog Web</h2>

<p>
    Welcome to the <strong>Book Catalog</strong> web interface!  
    This app allows you to manage a library of books, authors, genres, and track borrowings.
</p>

<hr />

<h4>🔧 What can you do?</h4>

<ul>
    <li><strong>View all books:</strong> Go to the <em>Books</em> page to see the current catalog</li>
    <li><strong>Add new books:</strong> Use the form at the top of the <em>Books</em> page</li>
    <li><strong>Edit or delete:</strong> Use the ✏ and 🗑 buttons next to each book</li>
    
    <li><strong>Borrowings:</strong> A page to view and manage who borrowed what is coming next</li>
</ul>

<hr />

<h4>🛠 Technologies used:</h4>
<ul>
    <li>✔ <strong>Blazor Server</strong> for the Web UI</li>
    <li>✔ <strong>Entity Framework Core</strong> for data access</li>
    <li>✔ <strong>MySQL</strong> database</li>
    <li>✔ <strong>Bootstrap 5</strong> for styling</li>
</ul>

<p class="text-muted mt-4">
    Use the navigation menu on the left to get started.
</p>
